#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.dtypes:1 of
msgid "Return the dtypes in the DataFrame."
msgstr "返回 DataFrame 中的 dtypes。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.dtypes:3 of
msgid ""
"This returns a Series with the data type of each column. The result's "
"index is the original DataFrame's columns. Columns with mixed types are "
"stored with the ``object`` dtype. See :ref:`the User Guide "
"<basics.dtypes>` for more."
msgstr ""
"这将返回一个 Series，其中包含每一列的数据类型。结果的索引是原始 DataFrame"
" 的列。混合类型的列以 ``object`` dtype 存储。更多信息请参见 :ref:`用户"
"指南 <basics.dtypes>`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.dtypes of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.dtypes:8 of
msgid "The data type of each column."
msgstr "每列的数据类型。"

